comments: Stewart (DET) places his forearm to Jokic's (DEN) side defending his drive to the basket and slightly extends his arm as he releases his pass attempt. The contact is marginal.
Stewart (DET) briefly places his hand against Green's (DEN) arm and immediately removes it as he gathers and prior to the start of his upward shooting motion.
Bey (DET) and Jokic (DEN) engage and disengage with one another during rebounding.
Stewart (DET) makes contact to Jokic's (DEN) shoulder which affects his shot near the rim.
Green (DEN) lightly brushes Cunningham's (DET) elbow defending his driving shot attempt.
Jokic (DEN) establishes himself in a screening position in Hayes' (DET) path and does not deliver contact.
Cunningham (DET) is in the paint for less than three seconds when the shot is imminent.
Jokic (DEN) makes marginal contact to Bey's (DET) side and does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Bey (DET) establishes himself in Morris' (DEN) path with his arm slightly extended and marginal contact occurs they disengage.
Lyles (DET) establishes himself in a screening position in Gordon's (DEN) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Cunningham (DET) places his forearm to Gordon's (DEN) side during his drive and releases as he gathers into his step back move.
Gordon (DEN) makes marginal contact with Cunningham's (DET) hand after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Green (DEN) and Lyles (DET) briefly engage and disengage while rebounding.
Lyles (DET) makes contact with the ball and cleanly dislodges it from Jokic (DEN) in the post before incidental contact occurs.
Green (DEN) places his forearm to Cunningham's (DET) front during his drive and makes incidental contact to his arm as he loses control of the ball.
Rivers (DEN) commits a take foul on Hayes' (DET).
Gordon (DEN) briefly places his hand against Lyles' (DET) body during the pick before correcting.
Green (DEN) moves laterally against Cunningham's (DET) path and makes incidental foot to ball contact during his drive to the basket.
Green (DEN) legally contests Cunningham (DET) jump shot attempt.  Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Joseph (DET) places his hand to Gordon's (DEN) side after gathering the rebound and marginal contact occurs as he releases his pass attempt.
Hayes (DET) briefly places two hands on Morris (DEN) as he moves toward the inbound pass and Morris is able to move through the marginal contact.
Cunningham (DET) commits a take foul on Morris (DEN).
Hayes (DET) commits a take foul on Morris (DEN).
Morris (DEN) and Joseph (DET) engage and disengage with one another off ball.
Cunningham (DET) commits a take foul on Morris (DEN).
Green (DEN) is the last person to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds. The possession is correctly awarded to DET.
